org.apache.ignite.internal.util.gridify

Class GridifyRangeArgument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.compute.gridify.aop.GridifyArgumentAdapter
      • org.apache.ignite.internal.util.gridify.GridifyRangeArgument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, GridifyArgument

    public class GridifyRangeArgument
extends GridifyArgumentAdapter
    Convenience adapter for GridifyArgument interface. This adapter used in grid task for GridifySetToSet and GridifySetToValue annotations.

    See Gridify documentation for more information about execution of gridified methods.

    See Also:
    GridifySetToValue, GridifySetToSet, Serialized Form
